{"tid":2157131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樹皮經濟】遼寧試行N-2點餐模式","createTime":"2020-08-14T22:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T13:08:16.000Z","uid":193077,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"908cd38be745f8d14d99b248653a991aaf23a5e8","tid":2157131,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:22:34.000Z","msg":"為響應中央政府樹立糧食危機意識的號召，遼寧發出倡議，針對大型聚會，餐廳可實行N-2點餐模式，即10位進餐客人只能點8個人的菜，不足時適當增加菜品，合理搭配，科學用餐，不攀比消費，不暴飲暴食，確保顧客吃好的同時，從源頭杜絕浪費。<br />\n<br />\n此前，湖北武漢、河南信陽、湖北咸寧等地的餐飲行業協會也曾發出&ldquo;N-1點餐模式&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"3775fd3a4c468900e26ddc7b2c5911d0ab7aa6e5","tid":2157131,"uid":263344,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:26:36.000Z","msg":"拍拖要絕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac6503e1b6d7f4a0f97a8e934217d7b84dc6551","tid":2157131,"uid":78336,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"3775fd3a4c468900e26ddc7b2c5911d0ab7aa6e5","tid":2157131,"uid":263344,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:26:36.000Z","msg":"拍拖要絕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:28:10.000Z","msg":"3p可以有一碟碟頭飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5ec3238e416bd7838a9757b030fb0461d0b792","tid":2157131,"uid":193077,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"dac6503e1b6d7f4a0f97a8e934217d7b84dc6551","tid":2157131,"uid":78336,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"3775fd3a4c468900e26ddc7b2c5911d0ab7aa6e5","tid":2157131,"uid":263344,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:26:36.000Z","msg":"拍拖要絕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:28:10.000Z","msg":"3p可以有一碟碟頭飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:31:09.000Z","msg":"再嘈就N-3"},{"pid":"cbfc74242279786d7e6566e75b310ea4f12833d